raw on key concepts presented in the previous chapters in the book to give an elementary proof of the recently proposed Böttcher-Wenzel conjecture. In addition, the appendix provides a preliminary discussion of the independence of the axioms of vector spaces. The book provides simple exercises for tutorials and more challenging exercises for student practice.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aMATHEMATICS / Algebra / Linear.2bisacsh1 aLIU, Wei-Hui, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aZHAO, Zhi, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022 Englishz978311099386808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022z9783110770445oZDB-23-DMA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2022z978311076825140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-3045-940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759830459423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759830459/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076825-1  EDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099386-8  EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  a